subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: The 16-year-old Belinda Bencic, playing in her first Grand Slam main draw match, beat 43-year-old Kimiko Date-Krumm in three sets at the Australian Open.
snippet: The 16-year-old Belinda Bencic, playing in her first Grand Slam main draw match, beat 43-year-old Kimiko Date-Krumm in three sets at the Australian Open.
